some signs that you like afi too much

1. you wear mesh shirts and tight pants to school     
2.you cut your sideburns like jades
3. you paint your room black and your door says "one big dark room"
4. your mom sings along to the woah parts in every song
5. when you see the charicature of AFI in Rolling Stone you scream SWEET JESUS in the middle of the grocery store
6.the school knows you will Not be in school march 11
7.you ex g/f became an ex-girlfriend because she didnt like AFI
8.when the names davey, jade, adam, or hunter are mentioned, no matter whats going on, THEY HAVE YOUR FULL ATTENTION
9.even the jocks know that AFI = a fire inside (because of all your shirts)
10.when a cop pulls you over, they see your license,registration, AND despair faction membership card!
11.there are constant fights between you and the members of other bands boards about AFI being WAYYYY BETTER!
12.your new girlfriend takes you to an AFI concert, yup, shes a keeper!
13.your brother who lives in a diferent state tries to win you AFI stuff all the time
14.lots of kids give you the sing the sorrow promo stickers because they know if they dont they will be stalked
15.your teachers fear the "fall children"
16.you sign your name with an x between initials
17.kids call you lil havok
18.NO SHOES NO SHIRT, NO PROBLEM...NO AFI?? WHAT THE HELL IS WRONG WITH YOU?!
19.even the wiggers in teh school know not to mess w/ my AFI
20.your local barber who is 60 knows what a devilock is
21.you call and complain to the mall muisc store that AFI is Not pop-rock (and after a month they make a punk section)
22.your girlfriends mom and tiny brother get front row with you in Toronto 
23.when kids fall asleep, AFI is written on their foreheads in sharpie marker when they wake up
24.the calandar at work that says "at a glance" in the upper left corner has most of "at a glance's" lyrics under it
25.everyone you know definetly knows what EBHC stands for
26.your parents are constantly harrasssed to take you to berkeley, CA
27.you make your grandma pick a favorite AFI song, the play it 900 times
28. you want to kill avril..wait you dont need to be an AFI fon for that!
29.your mom has caught you lip singing AFI in your bedroom, in your boxers,in front of a mirror, using a flashlight as a microphone...more than three times
30.when homies in your town try to blast rap, you show them up w/ the despair factor
31. you send death threats to the american film institute to change their name
32.you buy your local skatepark AFI cd's so they will play them while you skate/ride
33.if someone scratches your AFI cd's...they know they need to replace them then kiss your ass for a year or its curtains for them
34.on prom night as you wait for your date, you sit on the floor singing "waiting byyy theeee staiiiirs"
35. you kept your despair faction box
36.you wear your despair faction armband when your mom takes you to church
37. you have more makeup than your sister
38.when you get an AFI tattoo it takes weeks of thought, and while you are getting it done, you make the tattoo artist listen to AFI
39.your girlfriend wants to know where davey got his lipstick
40. your girlfriend thinks davey is pretty, and JADE IS HOT! and you agree!
41.at prom everyone slow dances to morningstar.
42.you become insulted if people ask if you listen to sum 41
43.son of sam does not register to you as a serial killer.

16 Signs You're Obsessed With AFI

1. Even though you hate maps, and everything pertaining to geography, you pull out the trusty atlas and look to see where Puget Sound is, all for the Jade.
2. You begin randomly chewing on the right side of your lip like Davey does during every interview, especially if your lips NOT pierced.
3. Whenever you write havoc (now suspiciously more often) you constantly misspell it as havok. (And the scary thing is, its unintentional.)
4. You begin to see the letters afi together everywhere, even in non-related words such as mafia.
5. Memorizing The Nightmare Before Christmas has become your sole after-school activity.
6. You're an avid AFI fan fiction reader/writer. You are also a subscriber to the mailing list.
7. You develop an intense, nonsensical hatred for the word palm.
8. If you're a guy, you begin to either grow asininely long sideburns, bleach your hair so its practically white, or begin training it into a devilock.
9. Your favorite foods slowly but surely become chicken, granola bars, croissants, grapefruits, broccoli, and Sno-Cones.
10. You actually understand what "the monster" is all about.
11. When making a scrapbook, the caption for you and your friends is, "Fall Children".
12. Your screen name is any one of the following: totalimmortal, morningstar, porphyria..anything to that effect.
13. When asked for your name, what time it is, the date, or anything, for that matter, you respond with, "Trouble, baby, trouble."
14. You develop an unexplained sense of dislike for anyone named Mark.
15. When asked, "Why are you so depressed?" or "What is your problem?" you reply with, "My whole life is a dark room. One. Big. Dark. Room." And succeed in scaring everyone away.
16. You sit down at your new Sims for PS2 and make an AFI household. The closest you could get to Davey was a red Mohawk, and it didn't really look like him, and Adam and Hunter, forget it. But Jade looks awesome. He has the pink tank top, black Dickie-like pants, the floppy brown hair, the emo glasses, and the SIDEBURNS! You got the sideburns! (I mean, no, what? Who would do that? That's pathetic)

everything you think of when you think of a
dragon - fearsome and invincible. Also, it is
greatly respected just because of that fact.
The dragon has a very protective aspect to it.
Even Jupiter reminds you of intense smashing
power. The dragon is almost always surrounded
by rain-bearing clouds and fog; and the
appearance of its constellation always signals
rainfall and lightning. It's also a symbol of
authority worn by the nobility and the imperial
class. Japanese Name: Seiryuu.
